## Compact Instructions

<!-- WHY: Squads have the most complex state — multiple agents, workflows, coordination. -->
<!-- WHY: Compaction without guidance loses the orchestration map. -->
<!-- WHY: [SOURCE: compact/prompt.ts:133-143] — Claude Code reads this section by name. -->

When summarizing this conversation, always preserve:
- The squad name (`{{PRODUCT_SLUG}}`) and full agent roster with roles
- Current workflow state: which workflow is active, at which step
- Agent coordination state: who is working on what, pending handoffs
- Capability index: which agent owns which capability
- Creator intent and the squad's strategic purpose from /fill
- Current MCS scores per agent and overall squad score
- Any inter-agent dependencies or blocking conditions

